.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>H - GATTACA</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Uma sequência genética é uma string S de tamanho N, composta pelos caracteres ‘A’, ‘C’, ‘G’ e ‘T’.</li>\n<li>Normalmente, um fio de DNA possui um segmento (substring) que se repete duas ou mais vezes, chamados repetições.</li>\n<li>Encontrar a repetição de maior tamanho em S.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/70fd404284f389e49ff563db9e06fb4b/fd84e/img21.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 56.44171779141104%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='img21' title='' src='/static/70fd404284f389e49ff563db9e06fb4b/a6d36/img21.png' srcset='/static/70fd404284f389e49ff563db9e06fb4b/222b7/img21.png 163w,\n/static/70fd404284f389e49ff563db9e06fb4b/ff46a/img21.png 325w,\n/static/70fd404284f389e49ff563db9e06fb4b/a6d36/img21.png 650w,\n/static/70fd404284f389e49ff563db9e06fb4b/e548f/img21.png 975w,\n/static/70fd404284f389e49ff563db9e06fb4b/fd84e/img21.png 1056w' sizes='(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/12f47b7d48f2d62f30a1d324f535c0d2/fd84e/img22.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 56.44171779141104%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-imag